          ],
          "COMMENT": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "The  absolute  C-12(g,p-0)B-11  reaction cross section",
                " was measured in the energy range of the giant  dipole",
                " resonance. The    magnitude    of    the    90-degree",
                " differential cross section,  which  has  an  absolute",
                " uncertainty of  about 12% ,  is  in disagreement with",
                " the one obtained by detailed balance  from  a  recent",
                " measurements of  (p,g-0) reaction cross section,  but",
                " is in reasonable  correspondence  with  the  combined",
                " data from Argonne and Stanford groups."
              ]
            }
          ],
